#description HearthKeep Hub Node - nRF5340 + ESP32-C6
#
# Hub node schematic for HearthKeep elder safety system.
# Components:
# - nRF5340 (dual Cortex-M33, BLE 5.0, Sub-GHz mesh coordinator)
# - ESP32-C6-MINI-1 (WiFi 6 + BLE bridge)
# - SX1262 (868MHz LoRa radio)
# - ILI9341 3.2" TFT display
# - MAX98357A I2S speaker amplifier
# - SPH0645LM4H I2S MEMS microphone
# - MCP73831 battery charger
# - AP2112-3.3V, AP6212-1.8V regulators
# - W25Q128 16MB flash
# - SD card slot
# - Emergency button, RGB LED, zone LEDs
#
# This is a placeholder - full KiCad schematic to be created.
